---
title: Prawn Peanut Noodle Stir-Fry with Tenderstem® Broccoli
description: A fast favourite, stir-frying is the perfect method to build flavour and cook quickly! This Prawn Peanut Noodle Stir-Fry heroes the veg and combines kejap manis, red Thai style paste and peanut butter to make a delicious sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R04_W48_UK_QV12033-23_Main__2low-c3b6a8ce.jpg
